Author: alexvilis
Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: INVESTING IN DROPBOX IPO  Good news friends: We are starting to accept applications for Dropbox IPO! That’s right — one of the best cloud storage services is going public at last. It would be no exaggeration to say that the whole market was waiting for this moment.  Dropbox hallmarks  Today Dropbox evidently dominates the race of cloud services. Even though it has to compete with such giants as Amazon and Google. Equally noteworthy is the fact that the company was incorporated just over 10 years ago, in 2007, — and managed to become one of the best from the best in the industry. The key strength of Dropbox lies in its shift towards the corporate segment. This provides for stable growth of paid subscriptions. For the moment the company counts over 300 thousand corporate clients. Totally the service has over 500 (!) million users from all over the world.  Dropbox has access to a very serious server infrastructure due to close partnership with Hewlett Packard Enterprise. This provides for scalability of the company in context of steady growing demand for storage place of a large bulk of data. Moreover, the service evolves also in terms of functionality expanding in mobile segment and extending the range of additional services, and this seems quite promising too.  Financial performance  Dropbox applies quite an unusual model of development and costs compared to other companies with such number of clients. It does not allocate great funds for marketing, but relies on self-service channels. Monetization is mainly due to corporate tariffs and additional services. As a result revenue of the company annually grows. Last year it was 1,1 bln $ compared to 845 mln $ in 2016 and 604 mln $ in 2015. Net loss of the company is decreasing at a steady rate — in 2017 it reached 112 mln $, which almost twice less than in 2016.  Public offering and deadlines  Dropbox will be listed at Nasdaq under the ticker symbol ‘DBX’. The company chose 12 investment banks including reputed Goldman Sachs and J.P. Morgan as underwriters of the project. The company expects to raise 500 mln $ during IPO, and its total capitalization may reach 10 bln $.  Investments to Dropbox shall be counted as mid risky. We forecast the average annual return at the rate of 80%. Minimum investment amount is equal to 5000 $.  The exact date of trading has not been announced yet, but it is more than likely to happen by the end of March.  https://medium.com/@Uttoken.io/investing-in-dropbox-ipo-d27f8c55d3d2

Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: So you guys need ICO for what? Company is in the market since 2009. What have you developed since then?  UT is a nice Russian company, you had your highs and deeps. But I still dont get it, why you guys need tokens? To pay trading fees? But your clients already pay you those trading fees. Will your clients have discounts on their fees, like it is on Binance for example? Use tokens to pay for consultations? - Dont get why you need tokens in order to do that. Cause you already have different Educational programs, which you sell to your clients for USD. Use tokens to pay for ads/clicks/articles? - so now you're some kind of social network? Create an decentralised exchange? - so... what use for UT tokens? Share profit? But I thought you have an utility token, not prfoit sharing.  You guys always try to make EVERYTHING. But when you tries to trade US stocks with one hand, push an ICO with another, create a social network with your leg, consult with ICO with another leg, make a trading platform with ... what you have left with??  I really wish you best luck, but better you concentrate on ONE thing and become best at. Hope this ICO wont fall like a brick, like 99% of other Russian ICOs, cause my personal opinion is that because of projects like that, which DONT NEED AN ICO in the first place, investors dont trust ANY Russian projects, even good ones.  Right now this ICO looks like a money grab, without a single need to integrate blockchain tech on this stage of development.  I specifically didnt post this right after ICO began, cause I really wish you best luck guys, even if that means to collect money from noobs on this market and buy a company's yacht))  PS And what in the universe means "dimension trading" of Anatoly R? Author: DRVX
Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: Here not posted this? Great info!  Digital Rating Agency http://digrate.com/en/ conducted an analysis of the United Traders project and assigned it a very high A2 rating.  According to experts, the concept and mechanism that developers offer are necessary for the further development of the entire cryptocurrency market, so the project seems potentially successful.

Author: A7373
Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: DigRate Rating Committee issued a Quality Rate High and A2 investment rating score to United Traders – medium-to-high probability of investment return, considerable sensitivity to market environment. The project team has a pragmatic approach to the problems existing in the cryptocurrency ecosystem and proposes to solve them by introducing a complex of products to the market, within the framework of a single platform. The concept and tools the developers offer are necessary for the further development of the entire cryptocurrency market. The platform modules created by United Traders already have working prototypes, which should allow it to attract large amounts of capital. The project conducts a massive advertising campaign. The team has presented a detailed road map and financial plan, specifying its targets. All of the above leave no doubt as to the serious intentions of the project’s developers and the possibility of implementing the project. Despite the undoubted competence of the developers, some aspects of the project raise questions. For example, it is unclear how the project plans to solve the problem of high loads on the global investment marketplace technically, as the transaction processing speed of the Ethereum network is rather low. Although the team has presented business models for each of the products, some elements still raise questions. DigRate also questions the potential attraction of banks to participate in cryptocurrency trading. The project team has not provided an analysis of the competitive environment, and has not disclosed information about the legal structure of the company. Similar solutions are being developed on the market, so the platform will be in a tough competitive environment, but we believe that the team has enough competencies to make a worthy product. Despite the developers stating that during the presale the project attracted several large investment funds, information about them has not been disclosed.

Author: A7373
Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: Know your customer (KYC) is the process of a business identifying and verifying the identity of its clients.[1] The term is also used to refer to the bank and anti-money laundering regulations which governs these activities. Know your customer processes are also employed by companies of all sizes for the purpose of ensuring their proposed agents, consultants, or distributors are anti-bribery compliant. Banks, insurers and export creditors are increasingly demanding that customers provide detailed anti-corruption due diligence information.

Author: superscalper
Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: The UTT purchase limits and the end of queue  Hello, dear traders!  Upon the launch of Pre-sale on uttoken.io, we received many questions related to the tokens purchase limits and what will happen if you transfer the amount not corresponding to the limits before the start of the primary Token sale (November 30). Let us try to clarify the situation.   Limits  At the moment, the Pre-sale phase is in progress. End of Pre-sale phase - November 30 05:59 GMT. The minimum purchase amount is 70 ETH. The maximum purchase amount is not limited.  The primary phase of Token sale starts on November 30 09:00 GMT. The minimum purchase amount is 0.1 ETH. The maximum purchase amount - will be announced between 6:00 and 09:00 GMT on November 30 at https://uttoken.io/ in our official Telegram channel: https://t.me/uttokenofficial  We give our strategic investors the opportunity to buy tokens so there is a probability of a deficit of tokens at the beginning of the primary Token sale on November 30 09:00 GMT. Orders issued by one user within the Pre-sale are summed up. The total amount determines the discount amount.  End of queue  White list is not provided, the sales of tokens will first come-first served, which means that the one to pay first will be the one to get the tokens. If by the time the money arrives from the buyer all the tokens have already been sold, such a buyer does not get tokens and can withdraw his money back.  If the buyer violates the minimum or maximum limit on Pre-sale or primary Token sale, then his funds fall to the end of the queue of the primary Token sale. кThis means that buyers who violate limits will receive tokens only if the untapped UTT tokens remain at the end of the main Token sale (December 24, 2017 23:59 GMT).  Recommendations:  In order to purchase the UTT during the primary Token sale you should:  1)  Register in advance at https://uttoken.io/. 2)  If you plan to pay in BTC or ETH, then go to https://uttoken.io/ at the start of the Token sale (30.11.2017 09:00 GMT), copy the purse address and make the transaction. 3)  In case of payment by bank transfer or a card, we recommend replenishing the dollar account on unitedtraders.com in advance. Go to https://uttoken.io/ to the beginning of Token sale (30.11.2017 09:00 GMT) and make a purchase of UTT by selecting "From United Traders account". This method will be available before the end of this week. 4)  If you want to purchase tokens for amounts over 70ETH, we recommend that you do this on Pre-sale, because the limit of the primary Token sale may be lower than this amount.  Please, remember the safety rules:  •  We will never send you a letter with an address for the transfer, all the data for sending funds are available only in the form of payment on the official website.  •  Check the browser address bar, the official website address: https://uttoken.io . No tokens can be purchased on any other sites.  •  Make sure that all data for the transfer is correct and do not forget about limits.   In case of any additional questions, please contact us via Telegram: https://t.me/uttoken_support_bot

Author: superscalper
Title: [ANN][ICO] United Traders: ⚡️ The High-End Solutions in Trading Technology ⚡️
Body: The UTT purchase limits and the end of queue  Hello, dear traders!  Upon the launch of Pre-sale on uttoken.io, we received many questions related to the tokens purchase limits and what will happen if you transfer the amount not corresponding to the limits before the start of the primary Token sale (November 30). Let us try to clarify the situation.   Limits  At the moment, the Pre-sale phase is in progress. End of Pre-sale phase - November 30 05:59 GMT. The minimum purchase amount is 70 ETH. The maximum purchase amount is not limited.  The primary phase of Token sale starts on November 30 09:00 GMT. The minimum purchase amount is 0.1 ETH. The maximum purchase amount - will be announced between 6:00 and 09:00 GMT on November 30 at https://uttoken.io/ in our official Telegram channel: https://t.me/uttokenofficial  We give our strategic investors the opportunity to buy tokens so there is a probability of a deficit of tokens at the beginning of the primary Token sale on November 30 09:00 GMT. Orders issued by one user within the Pre-sale are summed up. The total amount determines the discount amount.  End of queue  White list is not provided, the sales of tokens will first come-first served, which means that the one to pay first will be the one to get the tokens. If by the time the money arrives from the buyer all the tokens have already been sold, such a buyer does not get tokens and can withdraw his money back.  If the buyer violates the minimum or maximum limit on Pre-sale or primary Token sale, then his funds fall to the end of the queue of the primary Token sale. кThis means that buyers who violate limits will receive tokens only if the untapped UTT tokens remain at the end of the main Token sale (December 24, 2017 23:59 GMT).  Recommendations:  In order to purchase the UTT during the primary Token sale you should:  1)   Register in advance at https://uttoken.io/. 2)   If you plan to pay in BTC or ETH, then go to https://uttoken.io/ at the start of the Token sale (30.11.2017 09:00 GMT), copy the purse address and make the transaction. 3)   In case of payment by bank transfer or a card, we recommend replenishing the dollar account on unitedtraders.com in advance. Go to https://uttoken.io/ to the beginning of Token sale (30.11.2017 09:00 GMT) and make a purchase of UTT by selecting "From United Traders account". This method will be available before the end of this week. 4)   If you want to purchase tokens for amounts over 70ETH, we recommend that you do this on Pre-sale, because the limit of the primary Token sale may be lower than this amount.  Please, remember the safety rules:  •   We will never send you a letter with an address for the transfer, all the data for sending funds are available only in the form of payment on the official website.  •   Check the browser address bar, the official website address: https://uttoken.io . No tokens can be purchased on any other sites.  •   Make sure that all data for the transfer is correct and do not forget about limits.   In case of any additional questions, please contact us via Telegram: https://t.me/uttoken_support_bot
